	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />The unit will NOT have a cartridge port on it - it is an <strong>emulator</strong>, albeit an incredibly low-level one. Besides, said cartridge port would only be useful for <em>one</em> console, and this unit is going to support <strong>multiple</strong> systems (including but not limited to Atari 2600, Sega Master System, Colecovision).

		

